➜河南诗人樊国文：枯柏
http://www.sohu.com/a/421995369_100115135	55677
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200930/99f559b13a174d018de4c1e826c650a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>枯柏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/樊国文</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古柏干枯腐烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并没有丝毫哀叹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轰然倒地化土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依然无悔无怨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为她经历过探索</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奋斗抗争和磨炼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有过激动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快乐辉煌和奉献</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>从前</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用瘦弱的身躯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>陪着麻雀尽情游玩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用稚嫩的枝叶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>护着黄蜂上飞下翻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用稀疏的倩影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>伴着孩童的欢歌笑颜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当年</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
