<p><strong>3.图片来源网络，如有侵权，请联系主编删除。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200930/3611877910154644a1e6794ceee95cca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜江西诗人时差先生：仲秋
http://www.sohu.com/a/421996334_100115135	55937
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200930/f63b25c38bb94ccc8636b83e79306102.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>仲秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开花落 人间桂花香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯此时 花好月圆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天地间 歌舞蹁跹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寂寞的嫦娥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问天何年闲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别误了桂花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫耽搁流年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云中的飞月 闲外的清泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">差一棵树矣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人间望月 天上万万年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八月十五 空中皎月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大西北的风儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涌动翻天带地的水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彩云追月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲了一秋的云</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月老牵线</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
