➜广西诗人陈熠明：江南梦我醉烟波
http://www.sohu.com/a/421996993_100115135	59860
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200930/6b63bee602784c95a9397940b24f1c0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>江南梦我醉烟波</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•如烟雨梦在江南</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流波淡淡青蓝墨，古渡乌篷玉水湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">渐远重来飞往事，如烟雨梦在江南。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•风流墨幻水云间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缠绵细雨醉青烟，碧柳江边到客船。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦影仙姑桥上过，风流墨幻水云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•柳岸谁家在雨风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳岸谁家在雨风，流波荡漾问乌篷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云边墨色江南岸，水上飘红落影生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200930/709c4f2b1d014e0f9479c6e66060f97f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（四）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•回眸水岸又朦胧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回眸水岸又朦胧，小巷流连细雨中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远上兰舟波影幻，英姑伞下梦烟红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（五）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•天涯等落花潮影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落远清波柳岸拍，红姑水上雨烟来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯等落花潮影，梦里江南处处开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（六）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•渐去兰舟方远上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云边静岸柳摇风，等你约来正雨逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">渐去兰舟方远上，江南水岸梦烟生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200930/88549712e1824c75895ceb5072074a21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（七）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•栏边影幻落飞红</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥来等望水烟中，但愿乌篷细雨同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑面桃花风远去，栏边影幻落飞红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（八）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•乌篷静远看朦胧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乌篷静远看朦胧，柳岸凭栏意更浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫等时光将水负，江南雨色梦烟空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•人间梦幻雨江南</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云边静远秀峰环，柳岸千年玉水湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醉美流连烟影外，人间梦幻雨江南。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200930/ba77b61cae7748eeb0684c7bcca05ede.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·云烟水上醉红莲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥来忘返天涯去，静远兰舟梦雨烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉影流波飞墨幻，云边水上醉红莲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·江南梦我醉烟波</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青云岸上梳杨柳，水色桥边望雨娑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不舍红姑飞影恋，江南梦我醉烟波。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·雨里江南情荡漾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯望远风随愿，忘返乌篷落远开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雨里江南情荡漾，红姑梦幻水边来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200930/03bed5c579264a7d95c95a6e6f57dc23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200930/cd6c735692e4421b8720006ba04d1f5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200930/f3d8933ef962498cb89c50e9b8f74f4e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
